						<summary>

						<p>Slab built into the drain of Haḷekōṭa (a garden) outside the village.</p>						

						<p>12th century A.D.</p>						

						<p>This very badly damaged inscription is dated in the month Phālguṇa śu. 5, Sunday. Seems to register a gift of gold. The characters are of about 12th century A.D.</p>						

						</summary>
